item.content:encoded:
Tasty Blue is an adventure survival game. As a little goldfish, you have to eat fish food. Only in this way can you grow up and have the strength to escape from the fish tank. When you get bigger, you can even eat seagulls and ferocious sharks in the sea.
PCWASD or mouse to move.Mobile & TabletTap and slide to move.
